  1.Pe7-kiaN2 e5 oan-ke 
  Ah ! Cha2-khi2 chin-chiaN3 si7 ho2 e5 cha2-khi2. Phang-hoe e5 bi7 tui3 hoe-hng5 hou7 hong chit8 chun7 chit8 chun7 ah--lai5. Chhek-chiau2-a2 ki-bu2 ki-kiauh8, thiau3-bu2 ti7 tiaN5-cheng5 koe2-chi2 chhiu7 e5 tiong-kan. Jit8-thau5 tu2 chhut, kng-soaN3 chio3 kau3 thiaN-tiong. Hok-goan5 peh thau3-cha2 khi2-lai5 teh se2-bin7, giah8-thau5 khoaN3-kiN3 i e5 hau7-seN Thian-su3 ah tui3 toa7 mng5 jip8 lai5, bin7 ang5 ki3-ki3 khong7-khong7 tian, sin-khu chhau3 chiu2-hian3. Hok-goan5 peh chin siu7-khi3 tit8-tit8 me7--i. Thian-su3 ah teN3 bo5 thiaN-kiN3, chiu7 phin5 tui3 pang5-nih jip8 khi3. I e5 hu7-jin5 lang5 m7 kap i sio-chioh mng7, cho3 in tai7-ke khi3 chiah8 png7. Chit e5 hu7-jin5 lang5 si7 sim-pu7-a2 io-e5, seN cho3 koe3-tit khi3; kho2-sioh bo5 thak8-chheh, koh pak8 se3-kha; sou2-i2 tak8 hang7 khah nng2-chiaN2. Sio2-theng5 Po2-bi2 lau5, khui chhai3-toaN kap phiau5-chhiong-hui3 kiong7 15 khou beh lai5 theh8 chiN5. Ah ! Lun7 Thian-su3 ah, sit8-chai7 chin kho2-ouN3: chiah8 si7 san-tin hai2-bi7; chheng7 si7 chhoan5 leng5-lo5 phang2-si. In lau7-pe7 cha2-si5 u7 koa2 ke-hoe2 long2 hou7 i khai-liau2 khi3. Koh pau-chhi7 chit8 e5 cha-bou2 ti7 Thai3-lok8 hng5; bo5 siuN7 beh cho3 cheng3-giap8. HiaN-ti7 che7-che7 long2 phah-sng2 khi3; chi2 u7 chhun chit8 e5 sio2-moai7 kin-ni5 8 hoe3, kap hit e5 sim-pu7-a2 bou2 chit8 ke kiong7 5 lang5. Pe7-bo2 iu7 lau7, sio2-moai7 li7 se3-han3, pun2-sin m7 cho3 kang, koh phah-phun2 khai; sou2-i2 ke-lai7 chin siap, lau7-pe7 sui bong2 60 lian5 hoe3 lah, ia7 tioh8 siong5-siong5 chhut-khi3 cho3 sio2 khoa2 seng-li2-a2 lai5 thiN-thau5 thiap-boe2. Cha2-cheng5 Hok-goan5 peh si7 ho2-koe3 e5 lang5, in Lau7-pe7 bat cho3 Ti-koan7, i siau3-lian5 tong5-seng-na5 ia7 koaN7-phoa3 kui2-na7 kha. Siau3-lian5 e5 si5 kek8 hu3-ju7, beh chiah8-png7 tioh8 khau-cheng lui5-kou2; kau3 kin-a2 jit8 chiah8 lau7 lah chiah lai5 siu7-khou2 kau3 an2-ni, put-chi2 oan3-sin chheh-mia7. 
  Koh cha2-khi2 chiap-tioh8 chhai3-tiam3 khui toaN lai5 tho2-chiN5. Ah ! lau7-hoe3-a2 khi3 kau3 chhui3-chhiu phun3-phun3-phun3, kha-chhiu2 lak8-lak8-chhoah. (chit chun7 teh khi3 siuN7 ban7 lah ! chu7-se3 bo5 tiau-tok si7 pe7-bo2 e5 chho3-gou7) Hok-goan5 peh kong2 i m7 chai, i m7 heng5; chong2-si7 Hok-goan5-m2 kiaN liau2 nau7-su7, ia7 hou7 lang5 tiam3 mng5-khau2 jiang2 tho2 chiN5 phaiN2-se3, chiu7 kin2 jip8 khi3 lai7-bin7, chiong i e5 ou-kin theh8 lai5 giah8 chit8 lui2 ou-kin hoe, oa2 3 chiN5 tang7, tat8 oa2 16 khou, thau iap hou7 hit e5 lang5. ( khah siong5 lau7-bo2 khah gau5 seng7 kiaN2.) Tai7-khai3 Hok-goan5-m2 e5 kim-khi3 ia7 pian3 beh liau2 lah; chhun 2,3 hang7, taN ou-kin hoe koh hou7 lang5 ti2-siau3, chiu7 chhun 2 hang7 sio2-khoa2--e5 na7-tiaN7; m7-ku2 ui7 thiaN3 kiaN2 chiu7 bo5 sioh (Bo5 tek-khak an2-ni chiu7 ho7-cho3 thiaN3). 
  Hok-goan5 peh chai Hok-goan5 m2 chiong kim-a2 hou7 lang5 ti2-siau3, chiu7 koh khah bo5 hoaN-hi2 khi3, giah8 chit8 ki kun3-a2 tui3 in sim-pu7 e5 pang5-nih chiu7 jip8-khi3, chhut toa7 lat8 tui3 Thian-su3 ah chiu7 kong3 loh8-khi3. Siau3-lian5 ho2 kha-chhiu2, siam2-pi7 kong3 bo5 tioh8, Thian-su3 ah tui3 in tia e5 thui5-a2 chhiuN2 khi2 lai5, ka7 i bo7 hou7 to2. Lau7-hoe3-a2 siak tui3 hou7-teng7 loh8 khi3, ai chit8-e7 soa3 tiam7-tiam7. Hok-goan5 m2 ah ti7 chau3-kha thiaN-kiN3 sim-pu7 e5 pang5 phin5-phong3 kio3, lau7--e5 tit8-tit8 chhoh, chiu7 chau2 lai5 khoaN3. Kau3 tiong-thiaN, thiaN tioh8 lang5 siak to2 e5 siaN, chit8-e7 soa3 tiam7-tiam7. Chau2 kau3 pang5-mng5 khoaN3 lau7-e5 to2 ti7 pang5 lai7 e5 hou7-teng7 kha tiam7-tiam7, koh sim-pu7 teh khau3 A-pa o-oe3 ! Chiu7 chhiN-kiaN hoah kiu3-lang5, ( seng7-ti gia5 chau3, seng7-kiaN2 put-hau3). Chhu3-piN kong7-kong7 kun2, kin2 chau2 lai5 khoaN3, u7-e5 kin2 koeh, u7-e5 kin2 ka2 kiuN-bo2-chiap. Hok-goan5 m2-ah chit8-si5 sim-loan7, khauh8-khauh8 chong5. TaN ai3 chai Hok-goan5-peh chaiN2-iuN7 chhiaN2 khoaN3 e7 hoe5. 
  2.Phu5-long7 chia2 liu5-ti3 chhut-hoat 
  Kiu3 oa2 poaN3 tiam2-cheng, Hok-goan5-peh ah chiah hoe5-hun5, lang5 teh kiu3 in lau7-pe7 e5 si5, Thian-su3 ah cho3 i chhut-khi3 ( put-hau3 kau3 kek8). Au7-lai5 chhiaN2 kun5-thau5 sai-hu7 lai5 khoaN3, chiah8 siong-ioh8, to2 chiaN5 le2-pai3 chiah khi2-chhng5. Chhu3-piN khoaN3-kiN3 i chit ho7 kiaN2, chiu7 kap Hok-goan5-peh chham-siong5 kong2, sia2 pin2 tui3 koaN-thiaN jip8, hou7 i khi3 koaiN ti7 phu5-long7 chia2 e5 siu-iong5 sou2. Hok-goan5-peh khi2-thau5 chin m7 kam, au7-lai5 khoaN3-phoa3 ka3 bo5 hoat, chiu7 ka7 i jip8 pin2. Koh 3,4 jit8, keng2-chhat-thiaN chiu7 lai5 tiau7-cha, tai7-seng kio3 khi3 liu5-ti3 kui2-na7 jit8, mng7 pe7-bo2 e5 i3-kian3, long2 tang5-i3 chiu7 sang3 loh8 Hoat-iN7. Chhit goeh8 chhe 8 teng2 pou 8 tiam2 kong-phoaN3, i e5 ku7-an3 cho3 chhat8 poah8-kiau2 8 pai2, tiong-kan kan-im5 che7-che7 hang7; koh chit pai2 e5 ngou2-gek8, toa7-toa7 put-hau3. Chiu7 teng7 choe7 beh ka7 i koaiN ti7 Phu5-long7 sou2 6 ni5. Koat-teng7 7 goeh8 chhe 10 beh chhut-hoat. 
  7 goeh8 chhe 10 thau3-cha2 6 tiam2 goa7, sou2 u7 e5 hoan7-lang5 long2 khan beh khi3 che7 hoe2-chhia. In sou2 tiam3 e5 siaN5 si7 ti7 Po2-teng7, tui3 Hoat-iN7 liu5-ti3-tiuN5 kau3 chhia-thau5 oa2 3 li2 lou7. Hit jit8 70 goa7-e5 beh siu7 ke3-sang3 kau3 Phu5-long7 chia2 e5 siu-iong5-sou2; tiong-kan u7 chit8 e5 hu7-jin5 lang5, eng7 a-phian3 hun kiau2 moai5 lai5 thau7 si2 in ang; ia7 chit8-e5 si7 sio2-ti7 ui7 chai5-san2 saN-chiN e5 su7, thai5 si2 hiaN-ko, ka7 hiat hou7 chui2 lau5. Ah ! kong2 be7 liau2, long2 si7 sia7-hoe7 e5 chiu3-thang5. 70 goa7-e5 pai5 chit8 liat8; u7-e5 saN phoa3-phoa3, u7-e5 kha seN-thiaN3 noa7 hap-hap; u7-e5 toa7 tou2-thang2, bin7 ng5 phi-phi; u7-e5 giah8 koaiN2-a2, u7-e5 thau5-mng5 sam3-sam3. 7 tiam2 si5-cheng tan5, tak8-e5 tui3 kaN-gak8 chhut-lai5; nng7-e5 pak8 cho3-hoe2, chit8-tui3 chit8-tui3, long2 chheng7 ang5-saN koa3 thih-lian7, ia7 u7-e5 pho7 kiaN2 teh chiah8 ni. Ah ! chin kho2-lin5; u7-e5 gin2-na2 go7 kau3 san2 pi-pa, ia7 bo5 sim2-mih8 ni thang hou7 in chiah8. Hoe2-chhia 7 tiam2 45 hun beh chhut-hoat, sou2-i2 chin koaN2-kin2, khan3-siu2 chin heng5-gek8, chin ok, tit8-tit8 ka7 in thoa, kiaN5 khah ban7-e5, eng7 kha ka7 in cham3 (choe7 e5 po3-eng3, eng3-kai) long2 bo5 lin5-bin2 e5 sim. Ah ! Hiah e5 hoan7-lang5 e5 pe7-bo2, bou2-kiaN2 che7-che7 lai5 ti7 kaN-gak8 e5 mng5-khau2 teh tan2 beh khoaN3 i e5 kiaN2. Hok-goan5 m2-ah chhoa7 i e5 sim-pu7 kap i e5 cha-bou2 kiaN2 Bi2-hoai5-ah khia7 ti7 kaN-gak8 cheng5 lou7-piN e5 chheng5 kha teh khoaN3. Chit8-tui3 chit8-tui3 tit8-tit8 koe3, khoaN3 kau3 boe2-a2 te7 3 tui3, chiu7-si7 i e5 kiaN2 kap iau2 chit8 e5 thai5 lang5 hoan7 lian5 cho3-hoe2, Khan3-siu2 khan leh. Bo5 tiuN-ti5 Hok-goan5 m2-ah soa3 sim sng hau2 chhut lai5, teh kio3 i e5 kiaN2; sim-pu7, cha-bou2 kiaN2 ia7 lau5 bak8-sai2 (khah phaiN2 ia7 si7 kiaN2). Thian-su3 ah theng5 kha oat8 koe3 lai5 khoaN3, hou7 Khan3-siu2 ka7 I sai loh8 kong2 m7-chun2 i lou7-tiong kap lang5 kong2 oe7. Tiap8-a2-ku2 thou5-hun2 phong7-phong7 eng, chiu7 kau3 chhia-thau5. 
  Phu5-long7 chia2 siu-iong5 sou2 ti7 Bong5-kou2, kin7 Se-pi2-li7-a chit e5 siaN5 ho7-cho3 Mai7-mai2 siaN5. Hoe2-chhia tioh8 tui3 Pak-kiaN, TiuN-ka-khau2, Lun5-khou2 keng-koe3. Lou7-thau5 tioh8 che7 oa2 chiaN5 chap8 jit8 e5 hoe2-chhia. Hok-goan5 m2 khoaN3 kiaN2 hou7 khan3-siu2 koat, chiu7 na2 m7 kam sim, toe3 hoan7-lang5 e5 au7-bin7 tit8-tit8 kiaN5 kau3 chhia-thau5. Kau3 ui7 i2-keng 7 tiam2 30 hun, koh 15 hun cheng chiu7 beh chhut-hoat. Sou2-i2 bo5 hioh-khun3, liam-piN chit8 tui3, chit8 tui3, khan chiuN7 hoe2-chhia, si7 hou7 in che7 ti7 hoe3-but8 chhia, chhu tiu7-ko2 hou7 in che7, khoan2-thai7 in cho3 chhin-chhiuN7 ti. Kau3 tiam2 hoe2-chhia pi-a2 tan5, chiu7 khui chhia. Hok-goan5 m2 kap sim-pu7, cha-bou2 kiaN2 Bi2-hoai5 ah khui siaN khau3 kau3 oN3-oN3 kio3. Thian-su3 ah bin7 long2 bo5 oat8 chhut lai5 khoaN3 in, kaN2-si7 teh m7 goan7 in ka7 i jip8-pin2 a2-si7 teh iu-bun7. Bo5 cheng5 e5 hoe2-chhia tit8-tit8 kiaN5 khi3. Hok-goan5 m2 chit8 si5 soa3 hun7 to2 ti7 thou5-kha. 
  3. PeN7-chhng5 e5 bak8-sai2 
  Ti7 theng5-chhia-tiuN5 e5 Keng2-chhat kin2 chau2-oa2--lai5. Iah8-tiuN2 tai7-ke chiu7 chhah jip8 it, 2-teng2 e5 tai7-hap8-sek, hou7 i to2 ti7 nng2-nng2 e5 i2, kin2 iuN2 leng2 chui2 lai5 ka7 i u3 thau5-khak, kap heng-kham2, theng5 tiap8-a2-ku2 chiu7 chai lang5. Iah8-tiuN2 u7 chiong tam7-poh8 pho5-to5 chiu2 hou7 i lim, chiu7 cheng-eng. Che si7 lau7-lang5 hiat-khi3 soe-lam2 koh chit8-si5 koe3-thau5 hoan5-lo2, hoeh soa3 pho7-sim. I cheng-sin5 khi2-lai5, kap sim-pu7 cha-bou2 kiaN2 ian5-lou7 hau2. SiuN7-kiN3 ka-ti7 e5 phaiN2-mia7; cheng5 ho2-giah8, taN san3-hiong; kiaN2 lian5-lian5 si2, chhun chit e5 iu7 put-hau3, sui-bong2 oah8, iau2-ku2 chhin-chhiuN7 si2. 3-e5 oan2-jian5 chhin-chhiuN7 sang3-chong3 to3-lai5 chit8-iuN7. Chhu3-piN tai7-ke chin tong5-cheng5 lai5 an-ui3, kong2 Giok8-put-tok put-seng5-khi3. Ah ! He to7 si7 the3 lan2 ka3-si7, kin-tu2 na7 be7 ke2-piN3, put-si5 tiaN7 lou2-khi3, phaiN2 mia5-siaN, m7-tat8-tioh8 li7 lan2 hng7-hng7, ia7 seN-si2 si7 thian-sou3. Kin-tu2 na7 beh si2, ti7 chhu3-nih tiaN7 lam7-sam2 cho3, iau2 khah gui5-hiam2. Khi3 hia chiah8, khun3 chiau3-si5, koh cho3 kang un7-tong7. Phoa3-peN7 u7 phu5-long7-sou2 e5 i-seng pian7-pian7, pi2 chhu3-nih iau2 khah un2 ouh ! Tai7-ke chit8 chhui3 chit8 chih8 teh ka7 i khou2-khng3; tiong-kan ia7 u7 hit ho7 bu5-ti-e5 lai5 kau3 te3 kap i hau2 kau3 chhngh-chhngh kio3; chong2-si7 Hok-goan5 m2 thiaN tai7-ke sou2-kong2 u7 li2-khi3 chiu7 siu7 an-ui3. Koh Hok-goan5-peh ia7 teh me7 an2-choaN2 hiah m7-tam-su-iaN5, chiu7 m7 kaN2 hau2. 
  Chia chhiaN2 an3-ha7, lai5 kong2 Thian-su3 ah Ti7 chhia-lai7, Khan3-siu2 kau3 saN-tng3 chiong png7-oan5 chit8 lang5 chit8 oan5, iok-liok8 oa2 2 oaN2 png7, ia7 chiong chit8 liap8 kiam5-moai5-a2, kap tam7-poh8 chhai3-thau5-a2 hou7 in phoe3. Peng5-sou3 chit8 me5 khai tioh8 10-kui2 khou : ngou2-liu2-ki, ang5-sio-hi5, siu3-kiu5-oan5, hoah-kun5 lim chiu2, Chiok-hu7 koaN7-pan5; kin-a2-jit8 lai5 kau3 chia tioh8 chiah8 png7-oan5. Png7-oan5 e5 bi2 bo5 sim2-mih8 peh8, chho3-chho3 chiah8 tioh8 siap-siap; koh bo5 thng thang phoe3, hou7 i go7 kui2-na7 tng3. Keh jit8, si7 te7 ji7 jit8 e5 am3 si5, kau3 kin7 TiuN-ka-khau2 e5 ui7, tai7 ke khun3 tiam7-cheng7, tng hoe2-chhia teh kiaN5 e5 tiong-kan, khoaN3 hoe2-chhia kiaN5 chin ban7 chiu7 chhoah8 tng7 thih-lian7. Thian-su3 ah tui3 hoe2-chhia thang-a2 thiau3 chhut-khi3. In-ui7 chit sou2-chai7 ti7 chiaN5 le2 pai3 cheng5 u7 toa7 chui2, sou2-i2 lou7 u7 lioh8-a2 pang, chit-tiap8 teh siu-li2, sou2-i2 u7 kiaN5 khah ban7. Khan3-siu2 thiaN u7 lang5 thiau3 loh8 hoe2-chhia e5 siaN, chai u7 hoan7-lang5 to5-chau2, kin2 tiau7-cha, chiu7 chai si7 Thian-su3 ah. Kin2 thong-ti chhia-tiuN2 theng5-chhia. Tai7-ke kin2 loh8 lai5 chhoe7. Khan3-siu2 tit8-tit8 pun5 hui-siong5 keng2-kai3 e5 pi-a2, kiaN-chheN2 ti7 kang-liau5 siu-li2 hoe2-chhia lou7-e5. Kin-a2-jit8 si7 chhut-hoat e5 te7-2 jit8, in-ui7 si7 12 me5, sou2-i2 u7 sio2-khoa2 goeh8, lou7 kng-kng. Thian-su3 thiau3 loh8 lai5 e5 si5 to3-kha e5 toa7 thau5-bu2 u7 tak chit8 khang chin toa7 khang, hoeh chim-chim lau5; m7-ku2 khoaN3 hiah che7 lang5 teh pau, pi-a2 ki-ki-kio3. Sou2-i2 m7 chai thiaN3 tit8-tit8 piaN3. Kho2-sioh am3-si5, lou7 bo5 sek8, chiu7 hou7 ti7 hia siu-li2 thih-lou7 e5 jin5-hu ui5-tioh8. Cheng3-lang5 ia7 ui7-tioh8 i loh8 chhia, tan2 kau3 13 cha2-khi2 chiah koh khi2-kiaN5. Pun2 tioh8 koaiN 6 ni5, taN tioh8 koaiN 8 ni5 (Tho2 phoe5 thiaN3). Koh 7 jit8 goa7 chiu7 kau3 Mai7-mai2 siaN5. Kau3 ui7 ke-lou7 e5 lang5, ui5-ui5 chhut lai5 khoaN3. SiaN5-nih e5 lang5, ti7 cheng5 jit8 khoaN3 sin-bun5, long2 chai chit8 e5 put-hau3 e5 chheng-lian5 kau3 TiuN-ka-khau2 e5 hu7-kin7 chau2-hoan7, sou2-i2 tai7-ke ai3 ka7 i khoaN3 seN cho3 sim2-mih8 khoan2. KhoaN3 liau2 u7-e5 io5 thau5, u7-e5 phui3-noa7, u7-e5 ka7 i gin5, u7-e5 lau5 bak8-sai2, siuN7 tioh8 phah-sng3 hit e5 chheng-lian5 phiau-ti3, liu2-liah8, an2-choaN2 e7 put-hau3 koh chau2-hoan7. Thian-su3 ah pai2-a7-pai2, sou2-i2 lang5 long2 e7 jin7-tit, koh cheng5 jit8 sin-bun5 ia7 u7 i e5 siong7. Sou2-i2 chit8 si5 chin kian3-siau3 bin7 ang5-ang5, thau5 chhih-chhih, tit8-tit8 kiaN5. (Ia7 u7 liong5-sim). Koh tiap8-a2-ku2 chiu7 kau3 kaN-gak8 mng5. Chit e5 kaN-gak8 kui-bou5 chin toa7, chhiuN5 piah oa2 2 tng7 koan5, chiaN5 tng7 khoah. Mng5-khau2 u7 2-e5 peng giah8 chheng3 teh kou3. In-ui7 ti7 chia si7 koaiN hui-siong5 e5 hoan7-lang5, sou2-i2 peng-iaN5 u7 tek8-phai3 pou7-peng ti7 chia teh khan3-siu2. Kau3 mng5-khau2, chit8-e5 chit8-e5 koe3 tiam2-mia5 chiu7 jip8 khi3, ti7 chit lai7-bin7 chhah-sit8 to lan5-poe. 
  Si5-jit8 chin khoai3 koe3, tui3 jip8 lai5, bak8 chit8-choah8 liam5-piN oa2 4 ni5 lah. Iu7 chit8 jit8 Thian-su3 ah tioh8 tng5-chek-hu-su e5 peN7, chin siong-tiong7, tui3 tng5-a2 2 pai2 chhut hoeh, Gak8-i an3-sng3 i be7 ho2 lah. Hit-si5 chhin-chhiuN7 beh si2 liong5-sim hoat-hian7, siuN7 tioh8 i e5 pe7-bo2, koh chhin-chhiuN7 koh khoaN3 in lau7-bo2 ti7 chhia-thau5 teh khau3 e5 khoan2 kau3 beng5-beng5. Tui3 an2-ni chit8-si5 ti7 chhng5-tiong lau5 bak8-sai2, siuN7 kong2, Chit pang ThiN na7 hou7 i e7 ho2 khi2--lai5, i tek-khak beh ke2-piN3 lai5 iu2-hau3; m7-ku2 peN7 i2-keng chiah siong-tiong7. 
  4.Bo2-kiaN2 thi5-khau3 
  ThiN bo5 pang3-sak lang5, ki3-jian5 u7 chit8 sut-a2 hoan2-hoe2, peN7 chiu7 chiam7-chiam7 ho2. Kau3 goeh8-goa7-jit8 au7 chiu7 iu5-goan5 chiau3-goan5. 
  Ti7 KaN-lai7 e5 kui-ki2 si7 chin giam5. Mui2 le2-pai3 u7 chhiaN2 kui2-na7 e5 Bok8-su lai5 ti7 KaN lai7 kong2 to7-li2 hou7 hoan7-lang5 thiaN; chong2-si7 Thian-su3 ah kau3-kek8 nge7-sim, u7-si5 teh phoa3-peN7, chit hang7 hit hang7 m7-goan7 seng5-siu7 to7-li2. Chia chhiaN2 an3-ha7. 
  Kong2 in lau7-bo2 tui3 chhia-thau5 to3-khi3, kau3 kin-a2-jit8 4 ni5 lah, tak8-si5 liam7 i e5 kiaN2, koh tui3 hoat-iN7 thong-ti, kong2 in kiaN2 ti7 poaN3-lou7 chau2-hoan7, ke-teng7 2 ni5. Sim na2 kan-khou2, siuN7 tioh8 chiu7 hau2. Ia7 Thian-su3 ah e5 bou2, ti7 i boeh khi3 e5 si5 i2-keng u7 sin, khi3 liau2 chiaN5 poaN3-ni5, chiu7 seN chit8 e5 cha-bou2-kiaN2, in ma2 ka7 i ho7-cho3 Ma2-tan2 ah, i3-su3 si7 a-ma2 tit8-tit8 teh tan2 in a-pa5 to3--lai5, sim-pu7 na7 khoaN3 chit e5 kiaN2, ia7-si7 bak8-sai2 chun2 png7 thun. Kin ni5 4 hoe3, phut-phut thiau3, chin oah8-tang7,tit lang5 thiaN3; chong2-si7 m7 bat khoaN3-kiN3 lau7-pe7. Hok-goan5 m2 e5 bak8-chiu tiaN7-tiaN7 hau2 soa3 piN3 chin bu7; Hok-goan5 peh lau7-hoe3-a2 khi3 be7 kiam5-sng-tiN; ta-ke sim-pu7 ka7 lang5 se2 saN, giah8-chiam, lai5 tou7 koe3 jit8; sio2-moai7 Bi2-hoai5 ah kin ni5 12 hoe3 lah, sio2 hak8-hau7 2 lian5 seng, seN-cho3 chin sui2, koai, koh gau5 thak8-chheh, thang cho3 thong-ke e5 an-ui3. 
  Koh kong2 kau3 Thian-su3 ah tui3 peN7-au7, sim chit8 sut-a2 khah hoan2-hoe2, sou2-i2 khah kut-lat8 cho3 kang, tak8 hang7 chiau3 kui-ki2 u7 le2-sou3. Tui3 an2-ni Phu5-long7 sou2-tiuN2 chiu7 tek8-sia3 i chhun 5 ni5. Kau3 5 ni5 chiok, koaiN-kaN te7 5 ni5 e5 6 goeh8 boe2, tui3 kaN-gak8 u7 chit8 tiuN phoe kia3 to3 lai5, thiah khui chai si7 in kiaN2 Thian-su3 ah kia3-e5, thong-ke hoaN-hi2 kau3 lau5 bak8-sai2. Phoe tai7-khai3 si7 kong2 I ti7 hia gu7-peN7 hiam2 si2, ia7 taN i u7 hoan2-hoe2, kaN-gak8-tiuN2 beh hou7 i ti7 au7 goeh8 jit8 to3-lai5. Thak8-liau2 tai7-ke ma3-ma3 khau3, Hok-goan5 m2 chhut khi3 tiaN5 tiong-ng kui7 teh pai3 thiN-te7. 
  Kau3 7 goeh8 15 jit8 cha2-khi2 thiN phu2 kng, u7 chit8 e5 lang5 giah8 koaiN2-a2, chheng7 chhau2-e5, i-koan cheng2-che5, poe7 hit e5 pau-hok8-a2 tit8-tit8 tui3 toa7-mng5 jip8-lai5. Hok-goan5 m2-ah thau3-cha2 khi2-lai5 beh khui mng5, khoaN3 tioh8, chai si7 Thian-su3 ah ! 2 e5 bo2 a2 kiaN2 lam2 teh tit8-tit8 khau3. Thian-su3 ah kui7 loh8 kio3 kong2, An2-nia5! Goa2 u7 tek-choe7 thiN ia7 u7 tek-choe7 li2, goa2 chin kian3-siau3 m7 kaN2 kio3-cho3 li2 e5 kiaN2. Chit8 si5 kiaN-chheN2 Hok-goan5 peh, lai7-bin7 e5 lang5 chong5-chong5 chhut lai5. Ma2-tan2 ah 5 hoe3 ia7 kap lang5 khau3 kah ma3-ma3 kio3, chhu3-piN tai7-ke long2 chau2 lai5 khoaN3, m7 chai, kio3 si7 siaN2 lang5 cha-me5 si2. (Che si7 hoaN-hi2 e5 kek8-thau5). Chhu3-piN khoaN3 liau2, ia7 hoaN-hi2 kau3 be7 kou3-tit. Thian-su3 e5 bou2 ia7 chin hoaN-hi2, ui7 tiong7-hu chiu2 seN-koaN2 5 ni5, ia7 kou3 chit e5 kiaN2. Thian-su3 ah chiu7 pho7 kiaN2, chiong pau-hok8-a2 hou7 hu7-jin5 lang5 koaN7, tai7-ke jip8 thiaN nih, Ma2-tan2 ah kim-kim siong3 in lau7-pe7, m7 bat khoaN3-kiN3. Chit8 si5 ke-lai7 toa7 hoaN-hi2, chiu7 liam5-piN pi7-pan7 chiah8 cha2-tng3. Chiah8 pa2 thau2 pau-hok8, jip8 kaN-gak8 5 ni5 than3 oa2 300 khou, ia7 oh8 chit8 hang7 kang-ge7: e7 hiau2 cho3 tin5-i2, tin5-na5, kang-hu chin ho2. Chiu7 chiong chiN5 theh8 kau-tai7 lau7-pe7. Lau7-pe7 ia7 hoaN-hi2 kau3 lau5 bak8-sai2. Chit8 ke e5 hoaN-hi2 oh tit heng5-iong5, chhin-chhiuN7 beh si2 e5 ka-teng5 koh hok8-heng. Hok-goan5-peh chiu7 khi3 be2 chhai3, hit me5 pan7 chheN-chhau, chhiaN2 chhu3-piN lin5-iu7 saN-kap hoaN-hi2. 
  Thian-su3 ah ia7 put-chi2 lip8-chi3, tui3 chia khi2, beh jin7-chin keng-eng5 e5 khoan2-sit, chiu7 chiong sou2 u7 e5 chiN5, chit8 poaN3 khi3 be2 tin5, lai5 khui tin5-i2 tiam3, tiam3-ho7 ho7-cho3 Hok8-heng. Cho3 ni5-goa7 seng-li2 chin ho2, kho2-sioh chiN5 bo5 than3, soa3 chhoa7 se3-i5, se3-i5 tek-thiong2 long7-koan5, lai7-bin7 chhaN2-chhaN3 kio3, put-si5 oan-ke. Se3-i5 si7 siong-tong ho2 koe3 e5 lang5 e5 cha-bou2 kiaN2, koh u7 thak8-chheh. Sou2-i2 tit Thian-su3 ah thiaN3, khoan2-thai7 toa7 bou2 soa3 piN3 cho3 chhin-chhiuN7 cha-bou2-kan2, Ma2-tan2 ah beh chit8 chiam ia7 tioh8 tui3 in a-nia5 theh8. In-ui7 in lau7-pe7 kio3 Ma2-tan2 ah tioh8 kio3 se3-i5 an2-nia5, ia7 kio3 toa7-bou2 cho3 a-bo2. Ah! kho2-lin5, ui7 i siu7-khou2, khiN5-ke, chiu2 seN-koaN2 e5 thau5-mng5 kiat-hoat, kin-a2-jit8 long2 bo5 chit8 sut-a2 siuN7 tioh8. Tioh8 chu2-chiah8, lian5 se3-i5 e5 saN ia7 tioh8 ka7 i se2. Beh chhut-khi3 na7 bo5 mng7 se3-i5 u7 siaN to7 m7 kaN2 khi3; chong2-si7 Ta-ke khah thiaN3 toa7-e5: in-ui7 si7 i chu7 se3 io-e5, na2 cha-bou2 kiaN2 leh. Sou2-i2 u7 chit8 jit8, Thian-su3 ah chhut-goa7 pou2-hoe3, chhu3-nih 2 e5 toa7-bou2 se3-i5 oan-ke. Ta-ke u7 phah se3-i5. Se3-i5 m7-goan7, Thian-su3 ah to3-lai5 ka7 i tau5, Thian-su3 ah chiu7 phah toa7-bou2, chit8 ke loan7 chhau-chhau. Hit me5 toa7-bou2 chheh-sim tui3 au7-boe2 chhut-khi3, beh khi3 thiau3 loh8 chui2 (Khng3 lang5 m7-thang chhoa7 se3-i5, un2-tang3 be7 ho5). 
  5. Hui-siong5 e5 tiau7-cha 
  Thian-su3 ah in toa7-bou2 tui3 au7-boe2 mng5 chhut-khi3, ti7 in au7-boe2 u7 chit8 tiau5 khe-a2, lang5 goa7 chui2. I ia7 siong5-siong5 ti7 hia se2-saN. Kau3 khe-kiN5 khoaN3 tioh8 hiah e5 se2-saN e5 chioh8-thau5 ui7, na2 m7 goan7. Thian-su3 ah siu7-koaiN e5 si5 i ti7 hia se2-saN lai5 tou7 koe3-jit8, iuN2-chhi7 ta-ke-koaN e5 kan-khou2, chiu7 khui siaN toa7 khau3, siuN7 i kin-a2-jit8 chhut-si3 chin m7-tat8. SiuN7 i e5 phaiN2-mia7 cho3 lang5 e5 sim-pu7-a2, toe3 ang siu7-khou2 tam-iam5 un3-chhou3, chiu2 seN-koaN2, kau3 kin-a2-jit8 khah ho2-koe3, chiu7 hou7 se3-i5 khe2-cheh8 . Na2 siuN7 na2 m7-goan7; koh cha7-jit8 hou7 Thian-su3 ah phah, kong3 kau3 lau5 phiN7-hoeh bak tioh8 saN, khan saN-a2 khi2-lai5 khoaN3, na2 m7-goan7, chiu7 koat-i3 beh thiau3 loh8 khi3 si2; m7-ku2 chit8 sim siuN7 tioh8 seN3-mia7 kiaN2 Ma2-tan2 ah, kin ni5 7 hoe3, i chit8 lang5 na7 si2, kiaN2 chiu7 bo5 bo2. SiuN7 liau2 chiu7 koh un loh8 khi3 khe-piN hau2. 
  Li7 kui2-na7 chap8-pou7, u7 chit8 e5 lang5 am3-si5 teh he7 ko5, pang3 tio3 beh liah8 hi5, i siuN7 kong2 si7 cha-bou2 lang5 e5 ang si2 teh khau3, ia7 put-kai2 ki5-i3, koh si7 siau3 lian5 lang5, Sou2-i2 bo5 oa2 lai5 ka7 i khoaN3. Hu7-jin5 lang5 hau2-hau2 leh siuN7 kong2, Kin-tu2 oah8 ia7 bo5 chhai2 kong2, in-ui7 oah8-teh ma7 bo5 koan5 thang ka3 kiaN2, lian5 chit8 chiam-chiN5 ia7 tioh8 tui3 se3-i5 tho2, oah8 teh si7 peh8 cho3 cha-bou2-kan2. Tui3 an2-ni chiu7 khia7 khi2-lai5, chheh-sim thiau3 tui3 khe-te2 loh8 khi3. Hit e5 tng-hi5 e5 cha-pou lang5 kin2 chau2 lai5 khoaN3, i2-keng tim5 loh8 khi3 ah. Tng hi5-e5 kin2 chhang3-chui2-bi7 loh8 khi3 ka7 i gia5 khi2-lai5, chiah8 chin che7 chui2. I kin2 ka7 i pho7 khi3 khe-piN, ka7 i kho3 toa7 chioh8, hou7 i thou3-chui2 chhut-lai5, kai-chai3 iau2 teh chhoan2-khui3. 
  Kau3 10 tiam2 goa7 chhu3-nih Ma2-tan2 ah teh chhui3-ta tho2 beh chiah8 te5, chhoe7 bo5 bo2, teh hau2, phah chheN2 a-ma2, hit-tiap8 tai7-ke chiah chai lai7-bin7 bo5 lang5. Chhoe7 lai5 chhoe7 khi3 long2 bo5, kin2 khi3 po3 keng2-chhat tau3 chhoe7, chiah chhoe7 tioh8 ti7 au7 piah li2 goa7 lou7 e5 khe-kiN5, ti7 chhiu7-kha naih-a, naih. Kau3 ui7 tng hi5-e5 ia7 teh hoah kiu3-lang5, chin tu2-ho2. An2-ni tai7-ke chiu7 siat-hoat to3-khi3, sin-khu tam5 lok8-lok8, kin2 ka7 i oaN7 saN-khou3, kah hou7 i sio, choaN ko-le5 hou7 i chiah8, bin7 long2 peh8 si2-sat, keh chiaN5 goeh8 jit8 chiah iong2. Thian-su3 ah chit8 si5 ia7 chin kiaN, se3-i5 lian5 kiaN5 oa2 lai5 khoaN3 to7 bo5, cho3 i khun3, keng2-chhat chin siu7-khi3. Kio3 Thian-su3 ah khi3 phai3-chhut-sou2 soat-ju7, (se3-i5 thang khouN2-ouN3). Tui3 hia khi2, Thian-su3 ah ia7 chit8 sut-a2 khah m7-kaN2 koh phah i. 
  Chit8 jit8 u7 chit8 lang5, lai5 ka7 i be2 10 te3 teh-i2, kong2-ke3 e5 si5 tai7-ke ke-oe7, soa3 na2 jiang2 na2 toa7 siaN, Hok-goan5-peh ia7 chhut-lai5 hoah, be7 tiam7, soa3 sio-phah. Hit e5 lang5-kheh me7 i ¡§Phu5-long7 chia2 hoe3¡¨, goan5-seng3 chai3-hian7, khi2-kha ka7 i that chit8 e7, lang5-kheh to2 loh8-khi3, theng5 chin ku2 long2 bo5 ngiauh8, i chai si7 phaiN2-tai7 lah, chiu7 khi2-kha to5-chau2. 
  Lang5 khi3 po3-ko3, liam5-piN Kiam2-chhat-i kap Po2-teng7 siaN5 koaN-lip8 e5 peN7-iN7-tiuN2 lai5 giam7, giam7 liau2 pi5-chong7 phoa3-lih8, in-ui7 hit e5 lang5-kheh peng5-si5 tai3 ha7-siau, teng7-pi5 chin toa7. Sou2-i2 chho3-chhiu2 hou7 i phah si2. Hok-goan5-peh in chin kiaN. Keng2-chhat beh tui3 in tho2 Thian-su3 ah; na7 si7 m7 chai, in-ui7 i2-keng to5-chau2 lah. Tui3 an2-ni chiu7 chhut sin-bun5, oe7 heng5-siong7, in-ui7 si7 chian5-kho 8 pai2, ia7 bat ti7 phu5-long7 chia2 siu-iong5-sou2 5 ni5 ku7-hoan7. Sou2-i2 thong kok tek8-piat8 e5 chu3-i3, tek-khak beh liah8 kau3 tioh8. Chhut siuN2-keh, liah8 tioh8 e5 lang5 siuN2 kim 4 pah, lai5 po3 e5 lang5 siuN2 kim 1 pah. 
  6. ThiN-kong-toaN5 e5 chhiam-si 
  Thian-su3 ah tui3 phah si2 lang5 chiu7 tit8-tit8 chau2, ke2 mia5 oaN7 seN3, cheng5 seN3 Tan5 mia5 Thian-su3, chit pang ke2-cho3 Lim5 Thian-lai5, kin ni5 30 hoe3 cho2-iu7, chhui3-chhiu te2 chin ho2, sou2-i2 chiu7 lau5 chhui3-chhiu, jit8 bih, am3-si5 kiaN5, na7 kian3 hioh kheh-tiam3 chiu7 oaN7-mia5. Tit8-tit8 chau2 loh8-lai5 kau3 Lam5-kiaN, chia chhiaN2 an3-ha7. 
  Kong2 kau3 chhu3 nih, Hok-goan5 peh in nng7 lau7-e5 hoan5-lo2 kau3 be7 kong2 tit. Tiam3 siu-siu khi2-lai5. Se3-i5 khoaN3 Thian-su3 ah phah-si2 lang5 bo5 loa7-ku2 chiu7 to3-khi3 au7-thau5, chheng2 li5-ian5 choan2-ke3 (che si7 it-poaN se3-i5 e5 sim). Toa7-bou2 iu5-goan5 khiN5-ke. Kau3 Ma2-tan2 ah 8 hoe3 chiu7 hou7 i jip8 Sio2-hak8-hau7. Hit si5 Bi2-hoai7 ah 15 hoe3, Sio2-hak8-hau7 6 lian5. A-kou, sun-a2 tak8 jit8 chhoa7 khi3 thak8-chheh. Tui3 khui-tiam3, seng-li2 chhun oa2 3,2 taN3 chiN5, hou7 se3-i5 tut8 oa2 chiaN taN3 chhut-khi3. (se3-i5 khah-che7 si7 an2-ni) au7-chhiu2 chhun oa2 chit8 taN3, chong2-si7 ui7 phah-si2 lang5 hoat8-kim 500 khou, au7-chhiu2 chhun m7-chiaN5 chiN5. Chit ke 5 thau5 chhui3, ia7 si7 chin oh koe3, Thian-su3 ah e5 hu7-jin5 lang5 iu5-goan5 tioh8 koh ka7 lang5 se2-saN giah8-chiam lai5 tau3 khiN5-ke. Ia7 kin7-lai5 Hok-goan5 peh kau7 hoan5-lo2, koh lau7 lah, i tai3 chit e5 he-ku, sou2-i2 be7 koh cho3 seng-li2-a2 lah. Tui3 an2-ni sou2-hui3 chin an5-peN. Tak8-jit8 e7-pou si5-a2 thak8 chheh soah, Bi2-hoai5 ah kap sun-a2 siong5-siong5 khi3 khioh han-chu5, khioh-chha5, chia chhiaN2 an3-ha7. 
  Thian-su3 ah tit8-tit8 chau2 kau3 Lam5-kiaN. Beh chau2 e5 si5, ti7 toa7-kui7 lai7 sa 200 lian5 gin5, chau2 goeh8 goa7 jit8, lai5-kau3 chia chhun 100 cho2-iu7, u7-si5 iau-ki sit-tng3, bo5-bin5 phau2-lou7 ; koh tak8-si5 kiaN sim, liong5-sim chu7-chek. Siong5-siong5 am3-si5 khun3, bin5-bang7 lang5 tui kau3 ui7, hiahN8-chheN2. Sou2-i2 piN3 chin san2, sin-khu sou2 chhun e5 chiN5 na7 khai-liau2 khoaN3 beh chaiN2-iuN7. Sou2-i2 chiu7 siuN7 beh pian3 sio2 seng-li-a2 lai5 cho3, ia7 ai3 chai khoaN3 i e5 un7-tou5 chai2-iuN7, chiu7 khi3 Lam5-kiaN e5 ThiN-kong-toaN5 thiu chhiam. Chin seng5-sim be2 ho2 e5 chek-a2 kap siu7-kim. Thau5-chang-boe2 pang3 tit8-tit8, chit8 tian7 pai3 koe3 chit8 tian7. Jip8 kau3 siang7 au7 tian7 chiu7 sio hiuN, tiam2 chek, hian3 le2-mih8, chiu7 kui7-loh8 lai5 kiu5 Giok8-hong5 Siong7-te3 pi3-iu7, kiu5 liau2 chiu7 poah8 poe, mng7 khoaN3 i ti7-si5 e7 chhut-un7. Lian5 poah8 kui2-na7 pian3 long2 si7 siu7-khi3 poe. Chit8-si5 sim toa7 kan-khou2, i au7-lai5 he7 chin-che7 he7, ng3-bang7 Giok8-hong5 chhoa7 i chhut-un7, lian5-lian5 poah8 oa2 30 goa7 e5 poe, kau3-boe2 chiu7 in2 poe, (he si7 chu7-jian5; poah8 ku2, chhin3-chhai2 peng2, ma7 u7 poe). Au7-lai5 chiu7 khi3 thiu chhiam, chhiam-si e5 ku3 si7 kong2: 
