  Am3-tiong chiok-houN2, sit kong-hui, Beng5-hian2 kim-seng, chong5 hun5-li2; 
  Ku2-bok8 se3-sim5, ho5 put-tek, Kheng-sim it-chhat, leng5 se-kui. 
  Ke2-soeh si7 kong2, Am3-tiong chek-a2-hoe2 soa3 hoa-khi3, kho2-sioh thiN-teng2 kng-kng e5 kim-chheN, ia7 hou7 hun5 kham3-bat8 teh; Kiah8-thau5 siong5-se3 khoaN3, khah chhoe7 to chhoe7 bo5, chheh-sim chit8 e7 siuN7, leng5-kho2 tioh8 tng2-lai5 se-thian, i3-su3 si7 si2 khah ho2. Thian-su3 ah thak8-liau2 chit-si5 bin7 sit-sek, chai sou2 kong2 e5 i3-su3 si7 chin m7-ho2, sim-tiong am3-am3 chin kiaN, theh8 tam7-boh8 chiN5 hou7 hoe5-siuN7 thiam iu5-hiuN chiu7 chhut-lai5. Tui3 bio7-cheng5 e5 ki5-koaN kha koe3, khoaN3 chit8 tiuN kong-ko3, oe7 chit8 e5 siong7, toa7 sia2 2 ji7 Nia2-siuN2; ia7 e7-bin7 soat-beng5: kong2-khi2 Lang5 na7 liah8-tioh8 Tan5 Thian-su3 beh siuN2 kim 500 khou. KhoaN3 liau2 put-ti put-kak ka-ti7 thou2 chit8 e7 toa7-khui3 kong2, Ah ! Kin-a2-jit8 goa2 cho3 lang5, kau3 chia thiN beh choat8 goa2 e5 seN3-mia7 liauh, cham3 chit8 e7 kha, bak8-sai2 lau5 chhut-lai5. Tu2 teh kong2 chiah e5 oe7 e5 si5, au7-piah chit8 e5 be7 heng7-jin5-te5--e5 oa2-lai5 thiaN-tioh8 i kong2 an2-ni, chit8 taN3 heng7-jin5-te5 kin2 pang3-loh8-khi3, chiu7 tui3 au7-piah beh lai5 lam2--i. I u7 thiaN lang5 tng3 mih8 loh8 thou5 e5 siaN chiu7 oat koe3-lai5, tu2 hit e5 lang5 beh lam2--i, i chai-iaN2 oe7 kong2 liau2 lau3-khau2 lah, siuN7 beh chau2. Hit lang5 chin3-cheng5 ka7 i lam2-teh, 2 e5 tiam3 hia ian2. Hit chun7 tu2 thiN phu2-kng, khah bo5 lang5 koe3-lou7. Ian2 chin ku2, Thian-su3 ah u7 kun5-thau5 chiu7 kun2-khui, tui3 Lam5-mng5 tit8-tit8 chau2. Hit e5 lang5 hoah chhat8, kong2 chheng7 ou-saN, peh8 phang5-pou3-e5, hit-e5 chiu7-si7. Thian-su3 ah chai su7-se3 pek lah, lang5 tit8-tit8 piaN3 chhut ke-lou7, tiam3-lai7 e5 lang5 lai5 tau3 ui5. Tu2 chau2 kau3 Lam5-mng5-khau2 chit8 e5 oat-hang7-a2, i e5 ou-saN thng3 hiat-kak8; e5 ia7 thng3 khi2-lai5, pian3-oaN7 thng3-chhiah-kha chheng7 peh8 saN tit8-tit8 chau2, ia7 kap lang5 hoah chhat8. 
  7.Hok-khi3 kau3 mng5 
  Kau3 hia u7 che7-che7 hang7-a2 oat lai5 oat khi3, tui3 an2-ni lang5 soa3 jiok bo5 boe2 choa7. Tai7-ke soa3 tian-to3 hiam5 be7 heng7-jin5-te5--e5 peh8-chhat8; chong2-si7 be7 heng7-jin5-te5 e5 chin m7-goan7; m7-ku2 tui3 hit-tiap8 khi2 tai7-ke chin chu3-i3, si3-ke3 long2 phai3 tek8-bu7 tham3-cheng kap keng2-chhat, chheng7 peng5-siong5-hok8 si3-ke3 sun5 teh-tng. ChhiaN2 an3-ha7. Thian-su3 ah chai su7-se3 phaiN2, siaN5-lai7 tiam3-be7-tiau5, chiu7 khi3 kou2-but8-siong be2 kui2-na7 nia2 ku7-saN, u7-si5 chiu7 taN2-pan7 cho3 thou5-chui2 sai-hu7, u7 si5 chiu7 taN2-pan7 cho3 gia5-mih8 e5 khun2-kang ku-li2. Ia7 siaN5-lai7 m7-kaN2 toa3, chau2-khi3 tiam3 chhau2-te7, ia7 am3-si5 chiah khi3 chit8-keng eng7 chui2-la5-gia5 teh cheng-bi2 e5 bi2-kang-tiuN5 tau3 cho3 kang, keng-koe3 chiaN5 poaN3 ni5 long2 bo5 lang5 chai. Tui3 an2-ni keng2-lo5 e5 beng7-leng7 chiam7-chiam7 leng7. Chia chhiaN2 an3-ha7. 
  Kong2 chhu3-nih 5 lang5, khin5-khou2 teh koe3 jit8. U7 chit8 jit8 ti7 Po2-teng2-siaN5 e5 kau3-hoe7, ti7 hak8-hau7 hioh-joah8 tiong, u7 sun7 ki-hoe7 khui Ji5-tong5 ha7-ki5 hak8-hau7, mui2 jit8 toa7-lang5 gin2-na2 kui2 na7 pah lang5, kang2-su chin u7 gin2-na2-ian5, gau5 kong2 gin2-na2 kou2, oe7 ang-a2, koh ka3 sim-sek koa, ia7 u7 lu2 kau3-oan5 e5 im-gak8 chin gau5 teh pang-chan7. Sou2-i2 gin2-na2 3,5-e5 cho3 chit8-kun5 teh khi3 hu3, thau5 boe2 khui 3 le2-pai3. Tiong-cham7, oa2 8, 9 jit8 e5 si5 Bi2-hoai5 ah ia7 kap in sun-a2 chhoa7 jip8-khi3 thiaN. Hit e7-pou sin-seN teh kong2 chit-e5 kou3-su7, i3-su3 si7 kong2, lang5 u7 sim2-mih8 kan-khou2 na7 u7 chiu7 Ia5-sou, chiu7 e7 tit thau2-pang3, kiaN5 peN5-thaN2 e5 lou7 e5 i3-su3, thiaN liau2 Bi2-hoai5 ah toa7 siu7 kam2-kek. Chiu7 chiong chit chan5 su7 to3-khi3 po3 in nia5 chai. In a-nia5 chin hoaN-hi2, kong2, Kam2 u7-iaN2 u7 chit-chan5 su7, ti7 to2-ui7 teh kong2 ? Bi2-hoai5 ah ka7 i kong2, Ti7 pai3-tng5, mui2 e7-pou 2 tiam2 kong2 khi2 ia7 u7 toa7 lang5 khi3 teh thiaN. In lau7-bo2 chiu7 ka7 Bi2-hoai5 ah kong2, Bin5-a2-chai3 lan2 chiah thau chhoa7 lai5-khi3 thiaN, in-ui7 Hok-goan5 peh si7 kek8 sin3 put8, cheng5 bo5 thau5-lou7 ia7 bat khi3 cho3 hoat-koaN. Sou2-i2 chin thih-khi2, na7 thiaN lang5 ti7 lou7-piN teh pou3-to7, i tioh8 ka7 lang5 chhoh-chhoh leh, chiah kam-goan7 koh kiaN5-khi3, chin kau3-kek8 e5 oan3-hin7 to7-li2. Sou2-i2 in m7 kaN2 hou7 i chai. Lian5-lian5 khi3 thiaN 3, 4 jit8, ia7 ti7 pai3 6 e7-pou, gin2-na2 e5 chu7-chip8 i2-keng soah. Sin-seN khoaN3 toa7 lang5 chin che7 chiu7 koh chiong Iok-han7 3:16 chat cho3 te5-bak8 koh kong2 oa2 30 hun ku2 hou7 hiah e5 toa7 lang5 thiaN. Hok-goan5 m2 thiaN liau2 toa7 kam2-kek, be7-kim3-tit soa3 lau5 bak8-sai2. Kau3 soah i chiu7 oa2 khi3 mng7 sin-seN kong2, Sin-seN ah ! Chu2 m7-chai beh kiu3 goa2 a2-m7 ? Sin-seN khoaN3 i teh hau2 koh sou2 mng7 e5 oe7 si7 chin sit8-chai7, ia7 sim-tiong u7 loa7 iu-bun7 e5 khoan2-sit. Chiu7 chhiaN2 i jip8 au7-thiaN Bok8-su siok-sia3 lai5 che7. Koh kap i tam5-lun7 to7-li2, i mng7 i e5 cheng5-heng5, chiu7 chiong che7-che7 oe7 an-ui3 bian2-le7 i, u7 chhiaN2 i bin5-a2-jit8 lai5 le2-pai3. I in3 sin-seN kong2, m7-kaN2, in-ui7 tiong7-hu si7 toa7 hoan2-tui3 Ia5-sou kau3 e5 lang5. Tui3 an2-ni, bok8-su chiu7 chhiaN2 chit8 ui7 Eng-kok Kou-niu5 ka7 i kong2, Bin5-a2-jit8 chhiaN2 i khi3 chi2-moai7 in tau chhoa7 i lai5 le2-pai3. Hok-goan5 m2 kong2 ho2, chiu7 saN-si5 to3 khi3. 
  Hit me5-hng Hok-goan5 m2 chit8 sim chin hoaN-hi2 kong2, kin-a2-jit8 tit-tioh8 to7-li2. Lun7 tit-kiu3 e5 su7 iau2 boe7 beng5; m7-ku2 i siuN7 kong2 u7 Chu2 e7 the3 i thau2-khui tang7-taN3, kiam2-chhai2 e7 hou7 i e5 kiaN2 peng5-an to3-lai5. In-ui7 tui3 to5-chau2 kau3 taN, poaN3-ni5 khah-ke put-ti khi3-hiong3, m7 chai si2 a2 oah8. Sou2-i2 me5 jit8 bak8-sai2 lau5 bo5 ta. Kin-a2-jit8 thiaN Chu2 e7 kiu3 lang5. Oa2 ! Sim ke chin khui, sou2-i2 i ng3-bang7 lai5 thiaN to7-li2, chiu7 Ia5-sou e7 kiu3 i e5 kiaN2 peng5-an to3-lai5 (tu2-tu2 si7 an2-ni) sim chiu7 chin an-ui3; m7-ku2 chit8 sim chin kiaN, in-ui7 lau7--e5 m7-chai, ia7 bin5-a2-jit8 Kou-niu5 na7 lai5 kaN2 hou7 i phaiN2 siaN-sau3 chiu7 chin sit-le2. ouh ! siuN7 liau2 kui-me5 soa3 bian2-khun3. 
  Kau3 bin5-a2-jit8 Kou-niu5 kap chit8 e5 Chu2-jit8-oh8 e5 lu2 kau3-oan5 chiu7 lai5 chhoe7 i. Hit-si5 si7 7 tiam2-goa7, oa2 8 tiam2, i3-su3 si7 soa3 beh chio Bi2-hoai5 ah kap Ma2-tan3 ah khi3 thak8 Chu2-jit8-oh8, sou2-i2 liong7 khah cha2 chhoe7 in. Hok-goan5 peh chit nng7-jit8 u7 lioh8-a2 hou7 kam2-tioh8, sou2-i2 khun3 chin oaN3. Ti7 pang5-nih thiaN kiN3 u7 lang5 teh kong2 Ia5-sou e7 kiu3 lan2, m7 bian2 hoan5-lo2 chit hang7 hit hang7. Hok-goan5 peh tui3 bin5-chhng5 chhia khi2-lai5, khui siaN chiu7 chhoh, sa chit8 ki toa7 kong2 hun-chhoe, ham7-bin5 ham7-bin5, bak8-chiu hoe-hoe chiu7 tong7 chhut-lai5, khoaN3-kiN3 Kou-niu5 ti7 hia che7, chiu7 toa7 me7 ang5-mng5-hoan, hoan-po5, li2 lai5 chia beh chhong3 sim2-mih8? Hok-goan5 m2 sim toa7 kan-khou2, hiam5-thai2 hiah bo5 le2, lang5 i lai5 si7 ho2-i3. Tu2 teh kong2 e5 si5, Hok-goan5 peh chiong hun-chhoe-thau5 chiu7 ka7 i khian loh8-khi3, kong3 tioh8 thau5-hiah8, hoeh chim-chim lau5, in sim-pu7 kin2 tui3 Hok-goan5 peh e5 hun-chhoe ka7 i lak8-tiau5 leh. Ma2-tan2 ah chin kiaN, khui siaN tit8-tit8 khau3 A-nia5. Kou-niu5 kap Chu2-jit8-oh8 sin-seN chit8 si5 chin phaiN2-se3, soa3 chin bo5 i3-sin5. Chit8 lai7-bin7 chhiang7-chhiang7 kun2, bo5 phah-sng3 ho2-i3 soa3 oaN7 phaiN2-i3. 
